---
// VectorDBCompare.astro — Vector database comparison
---
<div class="vdc-wrap">
  <h3 class="vdc-title">Vector Database Comparison — 2026</h3>
  <div class="vdc-table">
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-row--h"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm">Database</span><span class="vdc-c">Type</span><span class="vdc-c">Scale</span><span class="vdc-c">Best For</span></div>
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-r1"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm"><span class="vdc-d vdc-d--cyan"></span>Pinecone</span><span class="vdc-c">Managed SaaS</span><span class="vdc-c">Billions</span><span class="vdc-c">Zero-ops, fast start</span></div>
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-r2"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm"><span class="vdc-d vdc-d--green"></span>Weaviate</span><span class="vdc-c">OSS / Cloud</span><span class="vdc-c">Billions</span><span class="vdc-c">Hybrid search, multi-modal</span></div>
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-r3"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm"><span class="vdc-d vdc-d--purple"></span>Qdrant</span><span class="vdc-c">OSS / Cloud</span><span class="vdc-c">Billions</span><span class="vdc-c">Rust performance, filtering</span></div>
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-r4"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm"><span class="vdc-d vdc-d--amber"></span>pgvector</span><span class="vdc-c">PG extension</span><span class="vdc-c">Millions</span><span class="vdc-c">Already using Postgres</span></div>
    <div class="vdc-row vdc-r5"><span class="vdc-c vdc-c--nm"><span class="vdc-d vdc-d--red"></span>ChromaDB</span><span class="vdc-c">OSS embedded</span><span class="vdc-c">Thousands</span><span class="vdc-c">Prototyping, local dev</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="vdc-rec"><strong>Start with:</strong> pgvector if you already run Postgres and have &lt; 5M vectors. Pinecone if you want zero ops. Qdrant or Weaviate if you need scale + self-hosting.</div>
</div>
<style>
  .vdc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .vdc-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .vdc-table{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;margin-bottom:1rem;overflow-x:auto}
  .vdc-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:120px 90px 70px 1fr;gap:6px;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:6px;align-items:center}
  .vdc-row--h{border-bottom:1px solid #334155;padding-bottom:8px;margin-bottom:3px}
  .vdc-row--h .vdc-c{color:#64748b;font-size:.58rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px;font-weight:700}
  .vdc-row:not(.vdc-row--h){opacity:0;animation:vdcIn .3s ease forwards;background:rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
  .vdc-r1{animation-delay:.05s}.vdc-r2{animation-delay:.1s}.vdc-r3{animation-delay:.15s}.vdc-r4{animation-delay:.2s}.vdc-r5{animation-delay:.25s}
  @keyframes vdcIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .vdc-c{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.66rem;font-family:monospace}.vdc-c--nm{color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
  .vdc-d{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}.vdc-d--cyan{background:#06b6d4}.vdc-d--green{background:#4ade80}.vdc-d--purple{background:#818cf8}.vdc-d--amber{background:#f59e0b}.vdc-d--red{background:#f87171}
  .vdc-rec{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #334155}.vdc-rec strong{color:#06b6d4}
</style>
